  "id": "RAW_50373bee",
  "title": "小米 Xiaomi Watch 5 体验：全智能手表，「智能」在哪？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTMwNDMwODQ0MQ==&mid=2653095700&idx=1&sn=dd7a3286e86da848a6c01c7b056cd56a",
  "date": "2025-12-26 07:49:00",
  "author": "极客公园",
  "siteName": "极客公园",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"ignored\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;margin-bottom:0em;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505612015\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;vertical-align:bottom;width:100%;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/8cu01Kavc5b8zQtYWPQ6iaNwPt8DvdOAr3C89ujytBwI4yHfiacCyqWfTCYfUGia8DBUrt6NS1X40Rveo4wyMSVOw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"341\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7533d075&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5b8zQtYWPQ6iaNwPt8DvdOAr3C89ujytBwI4yHfiacCyqWfTCYfUGia8DBUrt6NS1X40Rveo4wyMSVOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:25px 18px 18px;margin:-0.6em 8px 2em;background-size:100%;letter-spacing:0.3px;clear:both;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8em;background-position:100% 100%;background-color:rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;background-repeat:no-repeat;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1vpc\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">一块手表，想成为你生活的核心。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;margin-top:25px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6ooxu8\"><span leaf=\"\">作者｜张勇毅</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-indent:0em;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo21bx\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑｜</span><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">靖宇</span></strong></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:48px 8px 25px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1igo\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">整个 2025 年，小米智能穿戴生态，其实都围绕着「独立价值」这个概念来打造：这倒不是说这些智能设备追求的是脱离手机、独立运行，而是以小米眼镜为例的多款产品，都在对应的位置上，尝试交付区别于手机的独特价值，来在使用体验上，逐渐摆脱「手机的附庸」这种感觉。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oopsu\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 2025 年的岁末，小米通过全新发布的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Xiaomi Watch 5</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，在原本已经逐渐沉寂的全智能手表领域，扔下一颗新炸弹：这款被定位为小米最高端的全智能旗舰腕表，从原本的手机屏幕延伸，成为被赋予了「独立生命力」的终端设备。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"578\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=009000cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5b8zQtYWPQ6iaNwPt8DvdOArEicRJ38I6IxDY19ib4RbahQrnxhr9yZ5we0rjwBIDOyfXVsRlw6yUfDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1kun\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">小米 Xiaomi Watch 5 外观 ｜ 图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjmgjm561ql8\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1rz9\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1pyi\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">设计</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1hac\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">无论智能与否，对于高端腕表而言，材质的进阶往往是区分平庸与旗舰的第一道门槛。外观上，Xiaomi Watch 5 采用了极简的设计理念，47mm 的大尺寸表径在硬朗与优雅之间找到了绝佳的平衡点。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1jzd\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">在实际佩戴体验中，最令人印象深刻的是其实是全系标配的</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">双面蓝宝石玻璃：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">在行业内，通常只有顶级名表或极少数旗舰才会将蓝宝石玻璃同时应用于屏幕和底部心率盖板。这种人工蓝宝石玻璃给佩戴带来的除了更好的视觉通透感，还有更好的防刮耐磨性能，让手表在面对日常生活中的摩擦时更加游刃有余。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"385\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-w=\"3186\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b807feac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8cu01Kavc5b8zQtYWPQ6iaNwPt8DvdOAraJGBYhVpuJyou8EIhTm5QMBOKcM2H8rVJRfCJ6RzVEiaYTHgb8YduuA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oobx2\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">小米 Xiaomi Watch 5 机身采用双面蓝宝石玻璃 ｜ 图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1ag9\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这种轻盈的质感，配合 316L 不锈钢一体锻造的表壳，让 Xiaomi Watch 5 在拥有 1.54 英寸超大 AMOLED 屏的同时，依然能够提供轻如无物的佩戴体验。即使在户外强光下，其 1500nits 的峰值亮度也确保了屏幕信息的清晰可见，真正实现了雅奢设计与实用科技的共振。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjmgl9k2llz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oov8n\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oojr\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">EMG 传感器</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1m2y\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果说材质是手表的「皮囊」，那么交互逻辑就是它的「灵魂」。过去，智能手表的手势控制由于依赖传统的 PPG 或加速度传感器，往往被诟病为「识别不准」或「动作尴尬」。为了解决这个痛点，小米率先在 Xiaomi Watch 5 上引入了原本多见于高端医疗器械的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">EMG 神经电传感器</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。这种传感器能够绕过表面的震动捕捉，直接识别手部肌肉群产生的微小电信号变化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oojv3\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这一硬件底层逻辑的重构，直接带来了行业最高的 95% 识别准确率。通过这颗强大的心脏，Xiaomi Watch 5 实现了行业最多的 7 种手势交互。当你正在户外骑行，突然接到来电，无需停下车去操作屏幕，只需轻捏两次手指即可接听；当你在超市购物，手里提着购物袋无法腾出手时，只需轻巧地打个响指，手表便能一键弹出微信或支付宝的付款码。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"420\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7264150943396226\" data-w=\"7632\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d2b4885&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5b8zQtYWPQ6iaNwPt8DvdOArL6hJ1HvAFVEvOhzgWRZGLvQfj4DvmHYryZQsbTMSicjHeR9BXSo348Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"secondTitle\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1em;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 47, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oofsb\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">小米运动健康 App ｜ 图片来源：极客公园</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1qsb\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这种交互甚至延伸到了「人车家生态」的每一个缝隙。通过捏合拖拽手势，你可以像控制未来仪器一样远控小米电视或平板，在空中滑动即可调节音量或进度条；或者通过自定义手势，在推开家门的一瞬间打个响指，一键开启预设的「观影模式」，看着灯光渐暗、窗帘闭合、电视自动开启。这种「隔空控物」的流畅感，让手表成为了真正意义上的万物互联终端。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"title\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjmgm3lv1w42\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"isolation: isolate;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 36px;line-height: 1;letter-spacing: 0px;color: rgb(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oocfi\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6ooc2z\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">不再「大号手环」</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oopwj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">全智能手表的终极命题在于：如果没有手机，它还能为你做什么？Xiaomi Watch 5 给出的答案是「腕上小手机」。通过 eSIM 版本的支持，手表可以彻底脱离手机独立接打电话、收发信息以及独立支付。它内置了包括微信、支付宝、百度地图、网易云音乐、喜马拉雅在内的 70 多种主流 App，涵盖了影音、出行、社交等生活的方方面面。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\">