-light;\">这种极致的独立性，配合手表端全新的「超级小爱」AI 助理，让你随时随地都能通过语音询问天气、翻译外语或者控制智能家居。即使在运动后手抖点不准屏幕时，只需一声指令，小爱就能帮你开启空调。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo182h\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Xiaomi Watch 5 身上，健康监测不再是冰冷的数据罗列，而是温情的实时指引。针对力量训练爱好者，它推出了全新的</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">健身房模式</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1kfj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">通过表端的 3D 动画指引，它能够详细展示每一个训练动作的发力要领，引导用户进行针对性训练。即使是初入健身房的小白，也能在手表的指引下正确使用器械，并由手表自动记录动作次数、计数配重，最后生成详细的训练报告。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjmgu6oo1lbx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">而在生命体征的守护上，Xiaomi Watch 5 更是达到了医疗级的专业水准。它搭载了经过二类医疗器械认证的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">ECG 专业心电分析</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">功能。只需将手指按在表壳右下侧的触控按键上 30 秒，手表就能实时生成详细的心电图，并提供房颤风险预警。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"630\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0896226415094339\" data-w=\"5088\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8e4d7d9e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5b8zQtYWPQ6iaNwPt8DvdOArRpfU1k2O19unEmypjj1ichWj0ZReFMHhvA9A